org.matsim.contrib.socnetgen.sna.graph

Interface GraphBuilder<G extends Graph,V extends Vertex,E extends Edge>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractSparseGraphBuilder, GraphProjectionBuilder, SampledGraphProjectionBuilder, SocialSampledGraphProjectionBuilder, SocialSparseGraphBuilder, SparseGraphBuilder, SparseGraphProjectionBuilder, SpatialSampledGraphProjectionBuilder, SpatialSparseGraphBuilder

    public interface GraphBuilder<G extends Graph,V extends Vertex,E extends Edge>
    A GraphBuilder allows to create and modify graphs. It ensures that the connectivity of vertices and edges conforms to the definition of the underlying graph implementation.
    Author:
    illenberger
